snippet.textDisplay:
"The main road block is the power source"
Actually, it would be one of the 3 main road blocks. We are talking about laser here, so the 2nd problem would be the insanely powerful light emitters - how to cramp that necessary technology into this little handle? And 3rd problem would be - how to stop the light? You would need some other slightely impossible thing there, a freaking powerful shield emitter, also within this handle.


But I am sure you were realizing this by yourself just as well, you wanted to build a cool real life thing, getting as close to a light sabre as possible - and you did. I bow to your engineering skills, actually that battery pack is more impressive to me than the oversized glow stick. And that pack is at least as dangerous, if you screw up the wiring or some cell suddenly decides to mess around, you got yourself a very powerful bomb purse.
